<i>noun</i>: 후회 [후ː회/후ː훼], 회개 [회ː개/훼ː개], 참회 [참회/참훼], 뉘우침 [뉘우침] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>후회 [후ː회/후ː훼]</dt><br>
<dd>regret; remorse; repentance</dd><br>
<dd>이전에 자신이 한 일이 잘못임을 깨닫고 스스로 자신의 잘못을 꾸짖음.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of realizing that what one did was wrong and reprimanding oneself for having done it.</dd><br>
<dt>회개 [회ː개/훼ː개]</dt><br>
<dd>repentance; penitence</dd><br>
<dd>잘못을 뉘우치고 바르게 고침.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of regretting one's mistakes and correcting them.</dd><br>
<dt>참회 [참회/참훼]</dt><br>
<dd>repentance; remorse; self-reproach</dd><br>
<dd>잘못을 깨닫고 부끄럽게 생각하여 뉘우침.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of realizing one's shameful wrongdoings and regretting them.</dd><br>
<dt>뉘우침 [뉘우침]</dt><br>
<dd>repentance; penitence; contrition</dd><br>
<dd>스스로 자신의 잘못을 깨닫고 반성함.</dd><br>
<dd>Realizing one's fault and reflecting on oneself and one's behavior.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>